Create application that calculates average price of face mask:

1. in main method get price from user and add to list until input given by user is "exit"
2. create method that adds price to ArrayList and return true or false depending on whether it was added or not (handle conversion from string to double)
3. create method to get average of all prices from the list (handle situation if sum is zero, throw checked exception)
4. create a separate Tests class and test addPrice method and getAverage method
